      "ref": "master",
      "acceptance": {
        "enabled": false,
        "status": "blocked",
        "reason": "The module's cleanup_helper removes the rsyslog package between tests. In the harness's persistent Docker container model (PuppetCore pre-installed in the image), RPM database entries from the image build become corrupt, so rpm -e rsyslog fails with \"package not installed\" even though Puppet detects it as installed. This is a Docker copy-on-write filesystem artifact unique to the persistent container model."
      }
    },
    {
